 class MoveAlgorithm
          MoveAlgorithm is a super class for search algorithms.
 class NegaScout
          NegaScout, a subclass of MoveAlgorithm, is a negascout search algorithm.
 class PrincipalVariation
          PrincipalVariation, a subclass of MoveAlgorithm, is a principalvariation search algorithm.

          RandomGen, a subclass of MoveAlgorithm, generates a random move.
 

Uses of Constants in chess.core
 

Classes in chess.core that implement Constants
 class Board
          Board is simply a chess board layout containing all piece positions
 class ChessGame
          ChessGame contains all the necessary information for a chess game, such as the chess board, game and player parameters, timers, history, etc.
 class Coord
          Coord contains x and y coordinates for a piece's location in column and row, respectively.
 class Move
          Move contains the two coordinates for piece from and to location.
 class Piece
          Piece represents a chess piece
 class PieceCounts
          PieceCounts is used by ChessGame.
 class VirtualClock
          VirtualClock is a timer for the amount of time a player has left to move.
